~~~~~~~
General read me for development work
~~~~~~~


Models and textures
	Maya project setup
		- A folder has been added to the AngryGnome repo called ModelsAndTextures. When creating a new project in maya, go to File > Project Window, and set the location to this folder.
		- Then press accept

	Saving a Maya project
		- Save as ascii for backwards compatibility

	Other suggestions
		- turn on autosaves
			- windows > settings and preferences > preferences > files/projects > autosaves > enable
		- turn on infinite undo
		- turn on incremental save

